## Why weâ€™re doing this

We tested with schools the new service. Some schools said that when they registered their ECTs, it was 'too late' when they were seeing the details for the lead provider, delivery partner and appropriate body they were working with.

We think this is because:

- the delivery model for the early career teacher training entitlement (ECTE) is complex, and it helps remind them of the different parts
- there's a few different organisations they work with, and it can be difficult to remember them all
- it helps 

